more on the shadow side,

00:00:22.510 --> 00:00:28.390 align:middle line:10%
because it seems that
people are being misled

00:00:28.390 --> 00:00:30.970 align:middle line:10%
by certain forms of
spiritual teaching

00:00:30.970 --> 00:00:33.070 align:middle line:10%
that are out there right now.

00:00:33.070 --> 00:00:34.630 align:middle line:84%
You always have
to think positive.

00:00:34.630 --> 00:00:36.850 align:middle line:84%
You always have to
be in a good mood.

00:00:36.850 --> 00:00:38.620 align:middle line:84%
If you're not
succeeding, it's bad,

00:00:38.620 --> 00:00:41.020 align:middle line:90%
and success means making money.

00:00:41.020 --> 00:00:43.990 align:middle line:84%
And specifically I'm
talking about "The Secret."

00:00:43.990 --> 00:00:46.960 align:middle line:84%
"The Secret," of
course, as we both know,

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:48.640 align:middle line:84%
put out the idea
that the universe is

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:51.280 align:middle line:84%
like a cosmic gumball
machine, and all

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:56.620 align:middle line:84%
