00:00:59.020 --> 00:01:02.500 align:middle line:84%
What do you feel about this
idea that the universe is just

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:04.660 align:middle line:84%
going to grant you
whatever you want

00:01:04.660 --> 00:01:06.509 align:middle line:84%
and the idea of the
law of attraction?

00:01:06.509 --> 00:01:08.800 align:middle line:84%
People say, well, I don't
want to look at the bad stuff

00:01:08.800 --> 00:01:10.912 align:middle line:84%
because I'm not attracting
that into my life.

00:01:10.912 --> 00:01:12.370 align:middle line:10%
>>SPERRY ANDREWS:
As creatures tend

00:01:12.370 --> 00:01:15.310 align:middle line:10%
to withdraw our attention from
what's threatening and painful

00:01:15.310 --> 00:01:19.120 align:middle line:10%
and give it to what's
promising and pleasurable.

00:01:19.120 --> 00:01:21.790 align:middle line:10%
And if we divide our
attention that way,

00:01:21.790 --> 00:01:25.180 align:middle line:10%
we actually live in a more
contracted and suppressed state

00:01:25.180 --> 00:01:27.460 align:middle line:10%
because we need to give
equal attention to what

00:01:27.460 --> 00:01:28.610 align:middle line:10%
is threatening and painful.

00:01:28.610 --> 00:01:30.050 align:middle line:10%
I mean, it's part of our lives.

00:01:30.050 --> 00:01:34.780 align:middle line:10%
And we need to digest it and
integrate it into our psyches

00:01:34.780 --> 00:01:37.120 align:middle line:10%
both individually and socially.

00:01:37.120 --> 00:01:40.000 align:middle line:84%
And when "The Secret"
says, don't give attention

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:44.270 align:middle line:84%
to what is negative or dark
because you'll make more of it,

00:01:44.270 --> 00:01:49.120 align:middle line:84%
I think that really is
very serious misinformation

00:01:49.120 --> 00:01:51.610 align:middle line:84%
because you really need
to bring that which

00:01:51.610 --> 00:01:54.760 align:middle line:84%
is dark or negative or
unconscious to consciousness

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:56.890 align:middle line:90%
through being aware of it.

00:01:56.890 --> 00:01:59.809 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise you can't integrate
it and make it conscious.

00:01:59.809 --> 00:02:01.600 align:middle line:84%
>>DAVID: Well, let me
