for this unconditional love

00:34:28.560 --> 00:34:30.419 align:middle line:84%
and trust and unity
with our parents,

00:34:30.419 --> 00:34:34.980 align:middle line:84%
is by just sharing
undivided attention with us,

00:34:34.980 --> 00:34:37.590 align:middle line:84%
we feel their love,
and they feel our love.

00:34:37.590 --> 00:34:39.600 align:middle line:84%
And we feel this
beautiful happiness

00:34:39.600 --> 00:34:41.580 align:middle line:84%
as children with
our parents when

00:34:41.580 --> 00:34:44.639 align:middle line:84%
there's a proper
conscious relationship.

00:34:44.639 --> 00:34:46.800 align:middle line:84%
So we're practicing
a way of bringing

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:50.610 align:middle line:84%
about this unconditional eternal
love which is ever present,

00:34:50.610 --> 00:34:51.929 align:middle line:90%
always been present.

00:34:51.929 --> 00:34:55.449 align:middle line:84%
And we're gaining access to
it by giving attention to it.

00:34:55.449 --> 00:34:58.770 align:middle line:84%
So I look into your awareness
and you look into mine.

00:34:58.770 --> 00:35:01.550 align:middle line:84%
We look with both our
eyes, to begin with,

00:35:01.550 --> 00:35:04.080 align:middle line:84%
into the left eye
of our partner.

00:35:04.080 --> 00:35:08.790 align:middle line:84%
And we create partner pairs,
and we each gaze and speak

00:35:08.790 --> 00:35:11.910 align:middle line:90%
in turn, one at a time.

00:35:11.910 --> 00:35:16.830 align:middle line:84%
And over the course of
the minimum of 90 minutes

00:35:16.830 --> 00:35:20.790 align:middle line:84%
together-- but it's better to do
it for longer, like two hours.

00:35:20.790 --> 00:35:23.280 align:middle line:84%
Three or four hours is
even much, much better,

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:26.640 align:middle line:84%
because we have to
shift the momentum

00:35:26.640 --> 00:35:29.930 align:middle line:84%
and conditioning of this
separative way of paying

00:35:29.930 --> 00:35:30.730 align:middle line:90%
attention.

00:35:30.730 --> 00:35:34.860 align:middle line:84%
We have to change our
attentional style by attending

00:35:34.860 --> 00:35:37.500 align:middle line:90%
in an undevided way together.

00:35:37.500 --> 00:35:39.990 align:middle line:84%
So it's said that we're
going from the head

00:35:39.990 --> 00:35:43.410 align:middle line:84%
to the heart that's the greatest
journey we ever go through.

00:35:43.410 --> 00:35:46.080 align:middle line:84%
And we want to be able to
get the head and the heart

00:35:46.080 --> 00:35:49.750 align:middle line:84%
functioning together where
we're sentiently, emotionally,

00:35:49.750 --> 00:35:53.040 align:middle line:84%
psychologically, intuitively,
mentally experiencing

00:35:53.040 --> 00:35:57.000 align:middle line:84%
them as a unity, not
only alone but together.

00:35:57.000 --> 00:36:00.330 align:middle line:84%
So we're gazing into the
left eye to begin with.

00:36:00.330 --> 00:36:02.460 align:middle line:84%
And then after a while we
can gaze into both eyes.

00:36:02.460 --> 00:36:04.260 align:middle line:90%
Becomes very relaxing.

00:36:04.260 --> 00:36:06.475 align:middle line:84%
And we just take
turns in a group,

00:36:06.475 --> 00:36:09.390 align:middle line:84%
let's say a group
of eight people.

00:36:09.390 --> 00:36:12.030 align:middle line:84%
You don't speak
again after you've

00:36:12.030 --> 00:36:15.300 align:middle line:84%
spoken until everybody else
in the group has spoken.

00:36:15.300 --> 00:36:17.770 align:middle line:84%
And you just speak
about awareness

00:36:17.770 --> 00:36:20.070 align:middle line:84%
but by attempting
to describe it.

00:36:20.070 --> 00:36:22.410 align:middle line:84%
And it's virtually
indescribable.

00:36:22.410 --> 00:36:26.490 align:middle line:84%
But by attempting to describe
it, you become humbled.

00:36:26.490 --> 00:36:29.450 align:middle line:84%
You begin to notice your
awareness and your partner's

00:36:29.450 --> 00:36:34.160 align:middle line:84%
awareness as one
single awareness.

00:36:34.160 --> 00:36:36.480 align:middle line:84%
And you start describing
this sense of shared

00:36:36.480 --> 00:36:41.120 align:middle line:84%
empathic information and
interconnectedness and silence

00:36:41.120 --> 00:36:43.309 align:middle line:84%
and stillness that's
at the very core.

00:36:43.309 --> 00:36:45.350 align:middle line:84%
And you begin to feel it
in your hearts together.

00:36:45.350 --> 00:36:49.010 align:middle line:84%
You begin to feel it in every
cell of your body together.

00:36:49.010 --> 00:36:53.000 align:middle line:84%
And you go into this shared
sensitivity together.

00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:55.670 align:middle line:84%
And there's this pure
intelligence joy there.

00:36:55.670 --> 00:36:57.770 align:middle line:90%
Joy naturally arises.

00:36:57.770 --> 00:37:00.890 align:middle line:84%
And this loving kindness
and pure intelligence

00:37:00.890 --> 00:37:03.780 align:middle line:84%
and the separate self,
the separate ego,

00:37:03.780 --> 00:37:07.480 align:middle line:84%
which is normally so isolated
and afraid in seeing the other

00:37:07.480 --> 00:37:11.110 align:middle line:84%
and distrusting the other,
is nowhere to be found.

00:37:11.110 --> 00:37:13.340 align:middle line:84%
After about 15, 20
minutes of the exercise,

00:37:13.340 --> 00:37:15.740 align:middle line:90%
it's like, where did my ego go?

00:37:15.740 --> 00:37:17.230 align:middle line:90%
There's no ego anymore.

00:37:17.230 --> 00:37:18.850 align:middle line:90%
There's just experiencing.

00:37:18.850 --> 00:37:21.830 align:middle line:84%
So the subject and
the object disappear,

00:37:21.830 --> 00:37:23.840 align:middle line:84%
and they disappear
into the verb,

00:37:23.840 --> 00:37:26.900 align:middle line:84%
into the action of
experiencing, observing,

00:37:26.900 --> 00:37:29.630 align:middle line:90%
of feeling, of thinking.

00:37:29.630 --> 00:37:31.970 align:middle line:84%
The experience of
thinking is going on,

00:37:31.970 --> 00:37:34.370 align:middle line:84%
but it doesn't really
matter what you're thinking.

00:37:34.370 --> 00:37:36.950 align:middle line:84%
You experience the energy
of thinking, the energy

00:37:36.950 --> 00:37:44.000 align:middle line:84%
of sensing, feeling, being,
loving, existing, coexisting,

00:37:44.000 --> 00:37:46.640 align:middle line:90%
watching.

00:37:46.640 --> 00:37:51.290 align:middle line:84%
All these verbs become what
is central in the foreground

00:37:51.290 --> 00:37:53.990 align:middle line:84%
of your experience and
your shared experience.

00:37:53.990 --> 00:37:57.080 align:middle line:84%
And you explore that
with your friends

00:37:57.080 --> 00:37:59.850 align:middle line:90%
or whatever group you assemble.

00:37:59.850 --> 00:38:04.250 align:middle line:84%
And you just keep going
round and around like that

00:38:04.250 --> 00:38:07.640 align:middle line:84%
and keep talking
about awakeness.

00:38:07.640 --> 00:38:11.810 align:middle line:84%
And you'll find that you enter
into this cosmic consciousness

00:38:11.810 --> 00:38:14.630 align:middle line:84%
that would have taken you
days and days of meditation

00:38:14.630 --> 00:38:17.390 align:middle line:84%
to get to, and probably
would have never even gotten

00:38:17.390 --> 00:38:19.670 align:middle line:84%
there because you would
have been so overwhelmed

00:38:19.670 --> 00:38:21.950 align:middle line:84%
by the fragmentation
of your own thought.

00:38:21.950 --> 00:38:24.260 align:middle line:84%
But when you do it
as a group, your mind

00:38:24.260 --> 00:38:26.120 align:middle line:84%
goes silent almost
immediately because

00:38:26.120 --> 00:38:28.190 align:middle line:84%
of the magnitude of
your awareness and mine,

00:38:28.190 --> 00:38:29.690 align:middle line:90%
even right now.

00:38:29.690 --> 00:38:31.790 align:middle line:90%
I'm talking without thinking.

00:38:31.790 --> 00:38:35.370 align:middle line:84%
It's just this knowing
is able to speak.

00:38:35.370 --> 00:38:37.530 align:middle line:84%
And so it's really not
Sperry that's speaking.

00:38:37.530 --> 00:38:42.680 align:middle line:10%
It's our knowing that's able to
relate to itself through words

00:38:42.680 --> 00:38:45.020 align:middle line:10%
pointing at what is
really nonverbal,

00:38:45.020 --> 00:38:48.230 align:middle line:10%
which is really something
which really transcends

00:38:48.230 --> 00:38:52.010 align:middle line:10%
the limits of thought
and self-concept.

